{"tid":740531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇完呢段嘢重支持得落珀麗狗?","createTime":"2018-07-13T03:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T10:34:05.000Z","uid":163207,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9265237798286749894820c2fe78ccad109cdb","tid":740531,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T03:09:18.000Z","msg":"削減渡輪服務其中一個最直接影響，還是打擊當地樓價。居民文先生認為，一旦渡輪減班，無疑會打擊當地樓價，因為此舉會加深外界認為當地「交通不便」的壞印象，「聽到會削減服務，會想能否進入的呢？」當中又以要往中環或機場上班人士為甚：「當多了人知道這情況（交通問題），會考慮更多」<br />\n<br />\n死到臨頭重係講樓價,攬住層閪樓落地獄啦中產<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夾錢渣大飛出入啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c448527a8f57e9ebada558ddbdc1def120e54dd2","tid":740531,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"政府資助佢地托住個樓價"},{"pid":"266d69ff3738bdf694c1b019a5505ca109468178","tid":740531,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T03:16:07.000Z","msg":"樓價升就笑呵呵做中產,而家俾地產商撚就扮難民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初都係你哋炒樓養大佢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9351ccfaeff1acef728ad59ca1c976508e7fabd","tid":740531,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"39039b5ad8b14f1df35808a3cf2ae23cfee9647c","tid":740531,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"266d69ff3738bdf694c1b019a5505ca109468178","tid":740531,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T03:16:07.000Z","msg":"樓價升就笑呵呵做中產,而家俾地產商撚就扮難民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初都係你哋炒樓養大佢架<img src=\